@startuml general-activity-diagram.puml
title DVLD System - General Activity Diagram

start

:User logs into the system;
:User selects required service;
:User enters required data;
:System validates input data;

if (Input valid?) then (Yes)
  :System checks business rules;
  if (Business rules satisfied?) then (Yes)
    :System processes the request;
    :System updates database records;
    :System records audit information;
    :Display success confirmation;
  else (No)
    :Display business rule error;
  endif
else (No)
  :Display validation error;
endif

stop
@enduml